properties.Name: ProductIndirectLaborBudgetCostItem
properties.Description:
The individual cost items that are aggregated to make up the PRODUCT INDIRECT LABOR BUDGET.  

Ex:
- Salaries
- Healthcare Benefits
- Retirement Benefits
- Travel

Comparing Direct vs. Indirect Costs tell you how much of your labor costs go into actual making and providing services vs. labor costs to support these activities.

Columns.Name: ProductIndirectLaborBudgetId

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product Indirect Labor Budget Version.

Columns.Name: CostItemId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Cost Item.

Columns.Name: BudgetedCostItemAmount
Columns.Description: The amount budgeted/planned in the associated Budget for the Cost Item.

Columns.Name: ActualCostItemAmount
Columns.Description: The amount actually spent in the associated Budget for the Cost Item.
